'''天主教拉斯克魯塞斯教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Las Cruces}}；{{lang-en|Roman Catholic Diocese of Las Cruces}}）是[[美國|美國]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬於[[天主教聖菲總教區|聖菲總教區]]。1982年10月17日升為教區。<ref name="elevD">{{cite web |title=CRUCIENSIS* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19850817_cruciensis.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814123449/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19850817_cruciensis.html |archivedate=2019-08-14 |language=la |date=1982-08-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

範圍包括[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]南部十個縣。2010年有教友139,322人、45個堂區、81名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-en|伯多祿·巴爾達奇諾|Peter Baldacchino}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 15.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/15/190515b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811171811/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/15/190515b.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=en |date=2019-05-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|利則·拉米雷斯|Ricardo Ramírez}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 10.01.2013 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/01/10/0014/00040.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-08-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811203559/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2013/01/10/0014/00040.html |archivedate=2019-08-11 |language=it |date=2013-01-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

